title: MadHacks Fall 2023
description: Hackathons are a 24-hour event where teams of up to four have a friendly competition to create the best projects, products, and more. Food, prizes, mentorship, and events are all available. Hackathons give you the environment to make amazing, fulfilling projects in a short amount of time surrounded by driven individuals. Great for adding projects to your resume! Beginner-friendly with mentorship, talks, and workshops available.
